503
00:34:13,974 --> 00:34:15,374
Eu gosto.

504
00:34:16,981 --> 00:34:18,381
Certo.

505
00:34:20,911 --> 00:34:22,311
Aqui.

506
00:34:22,978 --> 00:34:24,378
Vamos pegar.

